            <h2>Why Hobbies Are Important</h2>
            <p>Hobbies can be helpful to everyone, no matter their age. You're never too old or young to find an activity to help you take your mind off of everyday things. Hobbies can help you find yourself, or even another person. They can bring people together and help you find a purpose. Most hobbies require creativity and developing creativity through a hobby can transfer directly into creativity at work. There are not many ways on the job to develop creativity and this skill is extremely important in today’s business world.</p>
